paths.<import>.allowImportNamesSection titled “paths.<import>.allowImportNames”
Specifies the set of import names that should be explicitly allowed.
SeeimportNamesfor the set of supported import name specifiers.
Only one ofimportNamesandallowImportNamesmust be specified.
{  "linter": {    "rules": {      "style": {        "noRestrictedImports": {          "options": {            "paths": {              "import-bar": {                "allowImportNames": [                  "Bar"                ]              },              "restrictPackagePrivate": "all"            }          }        }      }    }  }}
